# Debugging and Testing Examples
# Techniques for testing and debugging video processing pipelines

# 1. Basic functionality test
# Test that webcam capture and display work
webcam -> display

# 2. Test pattern validation
# Use synthetic patterns to test processing accuracy
test-pattern with (pattern: "checkerboard") -> edges -> display

# 3. Parameter testing
# Test different parameter values systematically
webcam -> blur with (kernel_size: 5) -> display

# 4. Performance testing
# Test frame rate with minimal processing
webcam -> display

# 5. Color space testing
# Verify color processing works correctly
webcam -> grayscale -> display

# 6. Filter chain testing
# Test multiple filters in sequence
webcam -> grayscale -> blur -> threshold -> display

# 7. Edge case testing
# Test with extreme parameter values
webcam -> brightness with (brightness: 100) -> contrast with (contrast: 100) -> display

# 8. Memory/performance stress test
# Test with high-resolution processing
webcam -> resize with (width: 1920, height: 1080) -> blur with (kernel_size: 9) -> display
